ZH: 各位同事，请注意，会议延期至下周。  
EN: Attention everyone, the meeting has been postponed to next week.  

ZH: 各位客人，请保持安静，不要打扰其他顾客。  
EN: Guests, please maintain quiet and do not disturb other patrons.  

ZH: 各位家长，让我们一起为孩子们的未来努力奋斗吧。  
EN: Parents, let's work together for a better future for our children.  

ZH: 各位读者，这本书是我最喜欢的一本小说。  
EN: Readers, this book is my favorite novel.  

ZH: 各位居民，请将垃圾分类投放到指定的垃圾桶里。  
EN: Residents, please dispose of trash according to the designated bins.  

ZH: 各位学生，今天我们要学习新的数学概念。  
EN: Students, today we will be learning a new math concept.  

ZH: 各位领导，我有一些建议想要向你们汇报。  
EN: Leaders, I have some suggestions that I would like to report to you.  

ZH: 各位职工，公司将举行年度活动，请准时出席。  
EN: Employees, the company will host an annual event, please attend on time.  

ZH: 各位运动员，大家加油，我们一定能赢得比赛。  
EN: Athletes, let's go, we can definitely win the game.  

ZH: 各位宾客，感谢你们出席我们的婚礼。  
EN: Guests, thank you for attending our wedding.  

ZH: 各位警察，新的安全措施将于本周实施。  
EN: Police officers, new safety measures will be implemented this week.  

ZH: 各位医生，感谢你们为患者提供无私的医疗服务。  
EN: Doctors, thank you for providing selfless medical care to patients.  

ZH: 各位乘客，请确保扣好安全带，飞机即将起飞。  
EN: Passengers, please ensure your seatbelt is fastened, the plane is about to take off.  

ZH: 各位志愿者，谢谢你们无私地奉献时间和精力。  
EN: Volunteers, thank you for selflessly dedicating your time and energy.  

ZH: 各位军人，感谢你们为国家的安全而奋斗。  
EN: Soldiers, thank you for fighting for the security of our country.  

ZH: 各位司机，注意安全驾驶，遵守交通规则。  
EN: Drivers, drive safely and obey traffic regulations.  

ZH: 各位同学，如果有疑问，请随时和老师沟通。  
EN: Classmates, if you have any questions, feel free to communicate with the teacher at any time.  

ZH: 各位病人，医院会尽最大努力为您提供最好的治疗。  
EN: Patients, the hospital will do its best to provide you with the best treatment.  

ZH: 各位买家，我们周五将举行特价促销活动，请踊跃参与。  
EN: Buyers, we will hold a special discount promotion on Friday, please participate enthusiastically.
